Echo-Service
############

This project is an easy example for remote communication 
with Akka 2.0.1.

You need SBT 0.11.3.

Quickstart:

$sbt
>update 
>run

Multiple main classes detected, select one to run:

 [1] org.scoding.echo.EchoClientApp
 [2] org.scoding.echo.EchoApp

Enter number: 2

$sbt 
>run

Multiple main classes detected, select one to run:

 [1] org.scoding.echo.EchoClientApp
 [2] org.scoding.echo.EchoApp

Enter number: 1

